title: I've Been Crockpotting for Ages Baby
description: The new word you can't say anymore, You Bet Your Wasabi!, Garbage Christmas Present Price is Right, Group Therapy, Jenny calls Dave out for doing something he shouldn't be doing during the show, we talk with a security person about her thoughts on the tragedy that took place at Travis Scott's concert, What do know that you shouldn't know?, War of the Roses, What's on your Radar?, and more!
